fulltitle: Joe Farnsworth Remembers the Masters:  Billy Higgins
title: Joe Farnsworth Remembers the Masters:  Billy Higgins
description: During this trying period, I’ve had some time to reflect. I’ve been thinking a lot about some of the masters of our music whom I love so much. Many of these great, I saw many times playing in the city. Some, I got to meet and even play with. Here’s something I put together about one of those very musicians, Billy Higgins. I hope you enjoy!
